{
  "texts": [
    "The key operations in ViS-MP are given as follows:",
    "where h i denotes the scalar embedding of node i, f ij stands for the edge feature between node i and node j. v!",
    "i represents the embedding of the direction unit mentioned in RGC.",
    "The superscript of variables indicates the index of the block that the variables belong to.",
    "We omit the improper angle here for brevity."
  ]
}